      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>A cross in relief is inscribed in a circle at the center of this lintel. Due to erosion of the stone, the reading of the last character as a chi, and thus the supplied letters of "Christ," is questionable. Dimensions refer to entire remainder of stone.</p>
         </div>
